cumented property? I wonder if `ClassTailor.noOptimize` is public or not. I should check how to handle this optimized behavior in my testing.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_xiDM5x5ZOP63xRVB80CKlO4g|fc_045b521fb3dcf2f9016a26c960e95c8193bbf221d640b3c75b", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/com.sun.xml.bind/jaxb-impl/2.2.3-1/src/test/java/com_sun_xml_bind/jaxb_impl/Jaxb_implTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "        public Callable<?> resolve(String id, Class targetType) throws SAXException {", "newText": "        public Callable<?> resolve(String id, Class<?> targetType) throws SAXException {"}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3120, "output": 1121, "cacheRead": 52224, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 56465, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780926789105, "responseId": "resp_045b521fb3dcf2f9016a26c945cd248193979ba510f6e75421"}}
